preference.preference_description: Used for configuring Teamcenter manufacturing process management technical portfolios. Defines which alias datasets display when loading alias files for IMAN_MEWorkInstruction pages. If not configured, all alias files are listed. Valid Values: Accepts multiple strings as values. Each string must be a valid Teamcenter alias dataset.
